OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fsettled evening with little cloud and
OL,7,Fplenty of evening sunshine. Winds will
OL,8,Fbe light and variable inland.
OL,9,FRemaining mild overnight despite the
OL,10,Flargely clear skies.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA fine and dry day, with
OL,13,Fbright sunshine and light winds.
OL,14,FFeeling hot, though temperatures could
OL,15,Fbe a degree or two cooler along the
OL,16,Fcoast in any sea breezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
