OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FLargely bright and sunny throughout,
OL,7,Fand notably hot on Tuesday.
OL,8,FTemperatures may start to decrease
OL,9,Ffrom Wednesday and into Thursday as it
OL,10,Fbecomes breezier, especially along the
OL,11,Fcoast.
